# Spring Boot — reservation-backend

## Stack

- Java **25**, Spring Boot **4.0.6**
- Spring Web MVC, Spring Data JPA, PostgreSQL
- OpenAPI: springdoc-openapi-starter-webmvc-ui **3.0.2**
- Base package: `co.ba.richarddv.reservation_backend`

## Project layout (current + target)

```
reservation-backend/                          # Maven module root
├── pom.xml
├── mvnw, mvnw.cmd
├── .mvn/wrapper/
├── src/main/java/co/ba/richarddv/reservation_backend/
│   ├── ReservationBackendApplication.java    # entry point (exists)
